data.description: WELCOME HOME TO TRANQUIL LIVING IN ORCHARD VIEW SCHOOL DISTRICT Nestled on a quiet street, enjoy this 4-bedroom, 2-bath home. Features include a spacious main level living room, currently used as a large dining area. The finished basement offers a cozy family room, perfect for movie nights or game days, a large bedroom, and a full bath. Also enjoy the 2-stall detached garage and fenced backyard making a safe place for children and pets to play.  Perfect for families and conveniently located near schools, parks, and amenities.  Schedule your showing today!  Buyer and buyer's agent to verify all information.
